## ZURB Foundation CSS Features
Here is list of ZURB Foundation CSS Features that included in NARGA WordPress theme:

*Notes: The italic words mean that features current NARGA not support*

***Grid***

* Grid

*Block Grid*

***Navigation***

* Pagination
* Breadcrumbs
* Sub Nav

*Side Nav*

***Buttons***

* Buttons

*Button Groups, Dropdown Buttons, Split Buttons*

***Forms***

* Forms

*Custom Forms*, *Switch*

***Typography***

* Type
* Keystrokes
* Inline Lists
* Labels

***Other CSS Components***

*Panels, Progress Bars, Tables, Visibility, Pricing Tables, Thumbs, Flex Video*

***Javascript Components***

* Alert Boxes
* Dropdowns
* Orbit
* Top Bar

*Magellan, Reveal, Tooltips, Interchange, Clearing, Joyride, Section, Abide
